---
export const label = 'Strategic partnership; punchy, direct';
---

<section class="py-16 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-xs uppercase py-6">Who is this for</h1>
    <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold mb-6">
      You've got the vision and you're looking for a strategic partnership.
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted">
      You have a clear idea for a product and the drive to see it through. What
      you need is a technical partner who can take ownership of the entire
      build&mdash;from solid foundational architecture to zero-downtime
      deployments&mdash;so you can focus on what makes your business unique. If
      that sounds like you, we should talk.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
